{
  "name": "AO-Planner-CE (4-view, faithful Path exec)",
  "description": "AO-Planner (AAAI 2025) affordances-oriented VLN-CE port on env_habitat. Faithful two-VLM Visual Affordances Prompting (Grounded-SAM 'ground' mask -> grid-sample -> VLM#1 proposer -> depth/intrinsics projection -> annotate -> VLM#2 PathAgent) + pure-FM framing (no ETPNav/TRM alignment). GroundingDINO+SAM run together in the detany3d server (model_grounding_dino__ground_mask). Fans the panorama into FOUR forward lanes (front/right/back/left = views 0/1/2/3, headings 0/90/180/270deg); each lane projects its own candidates and the 4 bundles fan into aggregate (gid + Image order = lane order). propose_prep (instruction-level proposer system prompt) and observe_ego (camera intrinsics) are shared across lanes. parse_proposal drops the foot-point anchor (id 0); resolve_action falls back to the most-forward valid candidate on an out-of-range action_id. gpt-5-mini both VLMs @ temp 1.0 / max_tokens 2000. D-2 (2026-06-17): multi-point Path execution restored via env_habitat__step_path (VLM#1 Paths -> per-route polar hops -> turn/forward with try-out sliding); C-2: GroundingDINO Swin-T OGC @ 0.4 'ground'; D-6: parse tolerance trimmed.",
